    <Header />
    <div class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class=
      "text-6xl mb-6 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-800">
        <span class="block xl:inline">Empowering</span> <span class=
        "block text-sky-600 xl:inline">Rural Democrats</span>
      </h1>
      <p class=
      "my-2 text-lg text-gray-500">
        We believe that Democrats need to fight everywhere&mdash;in every state, in every
        district, in every town in America to defeat the MAGA movement.
      </p>
      <p class=
      "my-2 text-lg text-gray-500">
        We believe that Rural Democrats need to be shown that their vote counts.
      </p>
      <p class=
      "my-2 text-lg text-gray-500">
        That's why we started Blue Wave America&mdash;to fund and train expert on-the-ground
        Democratic turnout staffers in rural counties in key swing states. We're on a mission to equip our staffers with cutting-edge voter turnout tools to get out the vote where Democrats have given too much ground to Republicans for far too long.
      </p>
      <div class="my-6">
        <Image
          src='/images/biden-and-trump.png'
          alt='Joe Biden and Donald Trump'
          width='900'
          height='150'
          class="rounded shadow mx-auto"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl py-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-800">
        Let's be clear:
      </h2>
      <p class="my-4 text-lg text-gray-500">
        MAGA Republicans like <strong>Ted Cruz</strong>, <strong>Marjorie Taylor
        Greene</strong>, <strong>Jim Jordan</strong>, <strong>Lauren Boebert</strong>, and
        more could be defeated as long as Democrats invest in rural communities...and they
        live in true swing states that President Biden needs in 2024.
      </p>
      <p class="yt-4 text-lg text-gray-500">
        That's why we're using our expert team of Democratic organizers to invest in
        flipping rural seats blue and increase rural Democratic votes in key swing states.
        We know full well that <strong>there are Democrats in those districts that need to
        be shown that their vote counts</strong> and we're fighting to make their voices
        heard.
      </p>
      <p class="my-4 text-lg text-gray-500">
        Not only will we show them that their vote counts, but we are also showing them how
        to organize and mobilize their own communities to make a difference.
      </p>
      <p class="my-4 text-lg text-gray-500">
        Our Blue Wave America plan uses:
      </p>
      <ul class="pl-12 my-4 text-lg text-gray-500 list-disc">
        <li class="my-1">
          Cutting-edge voter turnout technology
        </li>
        <li class="my-1">
          Expert on-the-ground rural Democrat organizers
        </li>
        <li class="my-1">
          Modern digital tools
        </li>
        <li class="my-1">
          A strong network of rural Democrat volunteers and activists
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="my-4 text-lg text-gray-500">
        Join us in our fight to defeat the worst Republicans in Congress, to keep MAGA
        Republicans away from the White House, and to give every American a voice in our
        system.
      </p>
    </div>


    <div class="grid gap-8 grid-cols-3 py-8 mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-800">
          We're fighting to elect
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500">
          Democrats that will stand for Democracy and will work to pass President Biden's
          agenda for the people.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12" role="list">
          {fightingForPoliticians.map(politician => <Profile politician={politician} />)}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="grid gap-8 grid-cols-3 py-8 mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-800">
          Our Work
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500">
          We fought hard in 2022 to hold the Senate and flip Red states and districts Blue and
          we'll keep fighting for Democracy <strong>Every Day</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12" role="list">
          {ourWorkPoliticians.map(politician => <Profile politician={politician} />)}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="relative overflow-hidden h-full py-6 mx-auto mt-5 sm:flex sm:justify-center md:mt-8">
      <div class="rounded-md shadow">
        <a class=
        "flex items-center justify-center w-full px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white border border-transparent rounded-md bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 md:py-4 md:px-10 md:text-lg"
        href="https://secure.actblue.com/donate/blue-wave-america-frontpage" target=
        "_blank">Donate Now to Blue Wave America</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="py-10 bg-gray-900 sm:py-10">
      <div class="relative isolate">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class=
          "flex flex-col max-w-2xl gap-16 px-6 py-16 mx-auto bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 sm:rounded-3xl sm:p-8 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:py-12 xl:gap-x-20 xl:px-20">
            <img alt="Rural Turnout Team" class=
            "flex-none object-cover w-full shadow-xl h-96 rounded-2xl lg:aspect-square lg:h-auto lg:max-w-sm"
            src="/images/rural-turnout-fund.png">
            <div class="flex-auto w-full">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
                Join Our Rural Turnout Team
              </h2>
              <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
                We are recruiting organizers and volunteers across the country to turn out rural
                Democrats in key swing states by learning and implementing tried-and-true voter
                turnout methods, innovative digital strategies, and creative relational organizing
                approaches.
              </p>
              <div class="flex mt-10"></div>
              <ul class=
              "grid grid-cols-1 text-base leading-7 text-white gap-x-6 gap-y-3 sm:grid-cols-2"
              role="list">
                <li class="max-w-md mx-auto mt-4 sm:flex sm:justify-center md:mt-4">
                  <div class="rounded-md shadow">
                    <a class=
                    "flex items-center justify-center w-full px-6 py-2 text-sm font-medium bg-white border border-transparent rounded-md text-sky-600 hover:bg-gray-50 md:py-4 md:px-10 md:text-lg"
                    href="https://forms.gle/34gepYHAuArnXNdf6" target="_blank">Become a Rural
                    Michigan Organizer</a>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="max-w-md mx-auto mt-4 sm:flex sm:justify-center md:mt-4">
                  <div class="rounded-md shadow">
                    <a class=
                    "flex items-center justify-center w-full px-6 py-2 text-sm font-medium bg-white border border-transparent rounded-md text-sky-600 hover:bg-gray-50 md:py-4 md:px-10 md:text-lg"
                    href="https://forms.gle/Lb7t9JxCrxLLWNrx6" target="_blank">Become a Rural
                    Wisconsin Organizer</a>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="max-w-md mx-auto mt-4 sm:flex sm:justify-center md:mt-4">
                  <div class="rounded-md shadow">
                    <a class=
                    "flex items-center justify-center w-full px-6 py-2 text-sm font-medium bg-white border border-transparent rounded-md text-sky-600 hover:bg-gray-50 md:py-4 md:px-10 md:text-lg"
                    href="https://forms.gle/vKdkGVrX7ghazJyL9" target="_blank">Become a Rural
                    Pennsylvania Organizer</a>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="max-w-md mx-auto mt-4 sm:flex sm:justify-center md:mt-4">
                  <div class="rounded-md shadow">
                    <a class=
                    "flex items-center justify-center w-full px-6 py-2 text-sm font-medium bg-white border border-transparent rounded-md text-sky-600 hover:bg-gray-50 md:py-4 md:px-10 md:text-lg"
                    href="https://forms.gle/uP8i1LYGjPXrGkHL8" target="_blank">Become a Rural North
                    Carolina Organizer</a>
                  </div>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div aria-hidden="true" class=
        "absolute inset-x-0 flex justify-center overflow-hidden -top-16 -z-10 transform-gpu blur-3xl">
          <div class=
          "aspect-[1318/752] w-[82.375rem] flex-none bg-gradient-to-r from-[#80caff] to-[#4f46e5] opacity-25"
          style=
          "clip-path: polygon(73.6% 51.7%, 91.7% 11.8%, 100% 46.4%, 97.4% 82.2%, 92.5% 84.9%, 75.7% 64%, 55.3% 47.5%, 46.5% 49.4%, 45% 62.9%, 50.3% 87.2%, 21.3% 64.1%, 0.1% 100%, 5.4% 51.1%, 21.4% 63.9%, 58.9% 0.2%, 73.6% 51.7%)">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <Footer />
	</body>
</html>
